snippet: If passengers on a delayed flight from New York to Charlotte, North Carolina, got a bit crabby, no one could really say they were being too shellfish....

headline.print_headline: Loose Crabs in Cargo Hold Delay New York Flight
headline.main: Loose Crabs in Cargo Hold Delay New York Flight

lead_paragraph: If passengers on a delayed flight from New York to Charlotte, North Carolina, got a bit crabby, no one could really say they were being too shellfish.
